{"type":"article_comment","id":259352,"parentType":"article","parentId":12969,"uid":12438,"contents":"@[url=https://pincong.rocks/people/NZRdlClr5] [/url]<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/NZRdlClr5\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">NZRdlClr5 </a><br>\n@ <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/Alicia\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Alicia</a><br>\n<br>\n你们之所以产生争论，是因为对民族的理解不对。<br>\n1. 民族是真实存在的，不是虚构的，民族间是有边界的<br>\n2. 民族既有文化属性也有血缘属性<br>\n3. 民族是以类似cluster的形式存在，民族的界限不一定泾渭分明<br>\n<br>\n为了帮助理解，下面贴一张网上随便找的东亚人DNA图，可以看到民族的血缘之间有边界，但边界模糊。而文化虽然无法测定，也是以类似有边界但边界模糊的形式存在。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/BMrhAmn_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BMrhAmn_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/BMrhAmn_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-22","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}